09:57:07.000Z","msg":"正視聽：<br />\n「人事登記處處長就會將該人資料轉交高等法院，用作編製陪審員名單之用。」<br />\n<br />\n只要大專畢業，就會自動收到一份「通知書」成為陪審員，但一般而言，大專畢業生只會收到由人事登記處發出的信件，要求填妥ROP 18表格以更新個人資料。高院會向人事登記處認可的合資格人士，發出「出任陪審員」通知書，若14日內沒有回覆，就會被加入名單。<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">若港人畢業後沒有收取過高院發出的出任陪審員通知書，可主動向人事登記處遞交ROP 18表格，以更新學歷資料。</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"8f96c780ba12b740dea04bcb681cc1f053453be3","tid":1740789,"uid":26307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190907/VGM64VHWQSYJFGOIFHJN4UPVU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190907%2FVGM64VHWQSYJFGOIFHJN4UPVU4%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNmDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=ae216d4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190907%2FVGM64VHWQSYJFGOIFHJN4UPVU4%2F&h=46b1eb18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190907/VGM64VHWQSYJFGOIFHJN4UPVU4/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係主動申請，而係如果有需要更新資料，必須更新，以免收唔到通知"},{"pid":"969880e7381190ece3de4470ff0a75ccceb658a2","tid":1740789,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c7c6d388f08d9c8ccb3fcd72645190ffe2c170dc","tid":1740789,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"鬼呀！"}]}